description:
Zhao Li, who is known as the youngest professor of medicine, accidentally crosses over to a world where women are superior to men. 

As a modern woman who cannot accept so many husbands and cannot watch men being enslaved, she has to resist the flirtation of her husbands and the deliberate seduction of countless other beautiful men, as well as farming, doing business, fighting with the people, fighting with businessmen, fighting with officials and fighting with female emperors...

It is really too difficult for me...>
